                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020113-35-off194 t18020113-35-cd195"></join>, two pair of silver salts, value 6s. a gold seal, value 1l. twenty-four silver handled forks, value 20l. two silver tish knives, value 4l. a silver soup-ladle, value 30s. a pair of silver sugar-tongs, value 9s. a silver snuffers-stand, value 30s. four silver saltspoons, value 12s. a silver salled-fork, value 1l. four silver sauce-ladles, value 2l. twelve silver tea-spoons, value 2l. eighteen silver table-spoons, value 10l. two silver watches, value 6l. and two silver snuff-boxes, value 2l. the property of 
                     
